* Pettigrew, Richard Franklin (1921). &quot;Triumphant Plutocracy: The Story of American Public Life from 1870 to 1920&quot;. New York: The Academy Press.
* Reed, John Calvin (1903). &quot;The New Plutocracy&quot;. New York: Abbey Press.
